# Add implementation start comment gh issue comment {STORY_NUMBER} \ --body "🚀 Starting implementation of story #{STORY_NUMBER}
**Session Start**: $(date) **Developer**: @me **Branch**: feature/story-{STORY_NUMBER}-{BRIEF_DESCRIPTION}"


