step.commit_template:

feat: {story title}

Implements story #{story-number}:
- {Key change 1}
- {Key change 2}
- {Key change 3}

Technical details:
- Added {X} new components
- {Y}% test coverage
- No breaking changes

Ready for: {Next story dependencies unlocked}

Closes #{story-number}

step.commands:

# Stage all changes
git add .

# Commit with detailed message
git commit -m "feat: {STORY_TITLE}

Implements story #{STORY_NUMBER}:
- {KEY_CHANGE_1}
- {KEY_CHANGE_2}
- {KEY_CHANGE_3}

Technical details:
- Added {X} new components
- {Y}% test coverage
- No breaking changes

Ready for: {NEXT_STORY_DEPENDENCIES_UNLOCKED}

Closes #{STORY_NUMBER}"

# Push changes git push origin feature/story-{STORY_NUMBER}-{BRIEF_DESCRIPTION}
# Create PR gh pr create \ --title "feat: {STORY_TITLE}" \ --body "## Summary
Implements #{STORY_NUMBER} - {STORY_DESCRIPTION}
## Changes - {DETAILED_CHANGE_1} - {DETAILED_CHANGE_2} - {DETAILED_CHANGE_3}
## Cross-Story Impact - **Components Available**: {New components ready for other stories} - **API Changes**: {New interfaces or breaking changes} - **Dependencies Unlocked**: Stories #{list} can now proceed - **Coordination Notes**: {Any coordination needed with other stories}
## Testing - ✅ All unit tests passing - ✅ Integration tests added - ✅ Manual testing completed - ✅ Cross-story integration verified
## Quality Metrics - **Test Coverage**: {X}% - **Performance**: {Impact assessment} - **Bundle Size**: {Impact if applicable} - **Accessibility**: WCAG 2.1 AA compliant
## Checklist - [x] Tests written and passing - [x] TypeScript types complete (no 'any') - [x] Documentation updated - [x] Lint and format checks pass - [x] Security standards followed (RLS, validation) - [x] Performance acceptable - [x] Accessibility standards met (WCAG 2.1 AA) - [x] Story completion handoff documented - [x] Sprint coordination updated
## Next Steps - **Ready for Review**: Code review and approval - **Dependent Stories**: {Stories that can now begin implementation} - **Integration Testing**: {Cross-story tests to run after merge}
## Screenshots (if applicable) {ADD_SCREENSHOTS_IF_UI_CHANGES}" \ --assignee @me \ --label "ready-for-review"

# PR creation auto-moves story to "Review" column # Update implementation phase gh issue edit {STORY_NUMBER} \ --add-field "Implementation Phase=Review"
# Add completion comment gh issue comment {STORY_NUMBER} \ --body "✅ Implementation complete and PR created: #{PR_NUMBER}
**Session End**: $(date) **Quality Checks**: All passing **Ready for**: Code review"

